data.description: Beautiful 3/2 on a large wooded and private lot. Vaulted ceiling with lots of windows brings the outside in. Florida Stone wood burning fireplace with mantle ready for those Christmas stockings.  Open dining room and kitchen offering lots of counter space ideal for parties. Florida room set up as another living area- a perfect place to hide with a good book. Sliding glass doors lead to the sparkling pool that is fenced and very private. Deck pavers offering patio areas for even the largest of families. Just a hop to downtown Mount Dora- known for its tree-lined streets and year around festivals on the shores of Lake Dora.  Roof was replaced in 2015  Air Conditioner was replaced in 2017  Hot water heater replaced in 2017  House replumbed 2017
